observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Local Chief Executive:

Consider conducting a comprehensive re-assessment of the needs for priority programs, projects and activities that will benefit the greatest number of constituents;
Cause the review of the unimplemented projects to determine responsiveness to the re-assessed needs;
Cause the allocation for redundant/irrelevant/unnecessary projects to be realigned to more responsive projects which are still subject for Sangguniang Bayan resolution;
Ensure that regular monitoring and feedback mechanism are in place for information and appropriate corrective action as may be necessary under the circumstances.

